{"tid":1216664,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本外相河野太朗回應香港示威","createTime":"2019-06-13T10:42:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T11:24:17.000Z","uid":41404,"like":29,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"7117257f69f06055c3129fbe18ce4021871aaad7","tid":1216664,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T10:42:17.000Z","msg":"河野太郎<br />\n@konotarogomame<br />\n香港の友人として、最近の情勢を大変心配しています。特に多くの負傷者が出ていることに心を痛めています。平和的な話合いを通じて、事態が早期に収拾され、香港の自由と民主が維持されることを強く期待します。"},{"pid":"ea6097003e7dd3e6111480800c601ca54ef91636","tid":1216664,"uid":41404,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T10:43:37.000Z","msg":"【日本外務大臣河野太郎回應近日香港的狀況】<br />\n<br />\n河野大臣：「作為香港的朋友，最近的狀況讓我非常擔憂。特別是看到很多的受傷者，令我感到份外痛心。通過和平的討論，我強烈希望情況能早日穩定下來，得以維護香港的自由和民主。」"},{"pid":"feab3dfae5fe4a618770351142d3f10619e62acf","tid":1216664,"uid":886,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T10:45:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dda49f89200e3423b33d9fe976da3ec1d2249b34","tid":1216664,"uid":41245,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T10:45:39.000Z","msg":"依個係英國嗰個聲明咋？"},{"pid":"cfff7042a90fe2da3b074a137142cb1ae34dc445","tid":1216664,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T10:51:15.000Z","msg":"俄國會唔會出聲，接收香港都好呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca9ed4fd85995af7092954783580bd45656b233e","tid":1216664,"uid":21545,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T10:52:42.000Z","msg":"日本仔咁不理世事都出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 自由世界大團結<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgm